transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan, mera manager nahi hai kya?
Executive: Sir, mai Ankita baat kar rahi hu senior manager Indiamart se, bataiye kya concern aa raha hai?
Customer: Hamare camera me isme lead hi nahi aa raha hai madam, bilkul lead hi nahi aa raha hai, hamara product efficient pack.
Executive: Efficient pack? Bataiye na batayenge aap? Efficient pack.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Okay. Sir Prashant aapke account manager hai, aap mujhe 15 minute ka time dijiye mai call back arrange karwa deti hu.
Customer: Okay.
summary:
